Pipeline summary
1. User asks an investment question such as "Should I buy NVIDIA?"
2. Orchestrator parses the prompt and extracts the target company/ticker.
3. Mavis retrieves market data from yfinance.
4. Henry + Leran retrieve the past four 10-Q filings and score filing tone.
5. Financial-calculation agent computes valuation and operating metrics.
6. Zipin writes the first complete report and attaches visualizations.
7. Jason edits the report to match a senior analyst standard and user needs.
